  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0001",
          "zh": "卷三 梁本纪第三",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0002",
          "zh": "末帝，太祖第三子友贞也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0003",
          "zh": "为人美容貌，沈厚寡言，雅好儒士。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0004",
          "zh": "太祖即位，封均王，为左天兴军使、东京马步军都指挥使。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0005",
          "zh": "乾化二年六月，太祖遇弑，友珪自立，杀博王友文，以弑帝之罪归之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0006",
          "zh": "以王为东京留守、开封尹，敬翔为中书侍郎、同中书门下平章事，户部尚书李振为崇政院使。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0007",
          "zh": "明年，友珪改元曰凤历。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0008",
          "zh": "二月，驸马都尉赵岩至东都，王私与之谋，遣马慎交之魏州，见杨师厚计事。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0009",
          "zh": "师厚遣小校王舜贤至洛阳，告左龙虎统军袁象先使讨贼。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0010",
          "zh": "是时怀州龙骧屯兵叛，方捕索之，王乃伪为友珪诏书，发左右龙骧在东都者皆还洛阳，因激怒之曰：「天子以怀州屯兵叛，追汝等欲尽坑之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0011",
          "zh": "」诸将皆泣，莫知所为。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0012",
          "zh": "王曰：「先皇帝经营王业三十餘年，今日尚为友珪所杀，汝等安所逃死乎！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0013",
          "zh": "」因出太祖画像示诸将而泣曰：「汝能趋洛阳擒逆贼，则转祸为福矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0014",
          "zh": "」军士皆呼万岁，请王为主，王乃遣人趣象先等。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0015",
          "zh": "庚寅，象先等以禁兵讨贼，友珪死，杜晓见杀。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0016",
          "zh": "象先遣赵岩持传国宝至东都，请王入洛阳，王报曰：「夷门，太祖所以兴王业也，北拒并汾，东至淮海，国家藩镇，多在东方，命将出师，利于便近。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0017",
          "zh": "」是月，皇帝即位于东都，复称乾化三年，复博王友文官爵。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0018",
          "zh": "三月丁未， 更名锽。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0019",
          "zh": "夏五月，杨师厚取沧州。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0020",
          "zh": "秋九月甲辰，御史大夫姚洎为中书侍郎、同中书门下平章事。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0021",
          "zh": "冬十二月，晋人取幽州。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0022",
          "zh": "四年夏四月丁丑，贬于兢为莱州司马。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0023",
          "zh": "武宁军节度使蒋殷反，天平军节度使牛存节讨之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0024",
          "zh": "贞明元年春正月，存节克徐州。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0025",
          "zh": "三月丁卯，赵光逢罢。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0026",
          "zh": "平卢军节度使贺德伦为天雄军节度使，分其相、澶、卫州为昭德军，宣徽使张筠为节度使。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0027",
          "zh": "己丑，天雄军乱，贺德伦叛附于晋。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0028",
          "zh": "邠州李保衡叛于岐，来附。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0029",
          "zh": "夏六月庚寅朔，晋王李存勖入于魏州，遂取德州。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0030",
          "zh": "冬十月辛亥，康王友孜反，伏诛。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0031",
          "zh": "十一月乙丑，改元。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0032",
          "zh": "耀州温昭图叛于岐，来附。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0033",
          "zh": "是岁，更名瑱。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0034",
          "zh": "二年春二月丙申，杨涉罢。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0035",
          "zh": "三月，镇南军节度使刘掞及晋人战于故元城，败绩，奔于滑州。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0036",
          "zh": "晋人取卫州、惠州。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0037",
          "zh": "捉生都将李霸反，伏诛。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0038",
          "zh": "夏六月，捉生都将张温叛降于晋。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0039",
          "zh": "秋七月，晋人取相州，张筠奔于京师，安国军节度使阎宝叛附于晋。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0040",
          "zh": "八月丁酉，太子太保致仕赵光逢为司空兼门下侍郎、同中书门下平章事。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0041",
          "zh": "九月，晋人取沧州，横海军节度使戴思远奔于京师。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0042",
          "zh": "晋人克贝州，守将张源德死之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0043",
          "zh": "冬十月丁酉，中书侍郎郑珏同中书门下平章事。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0044",
          "zh": "三年夏四月辛卯，右千牛卫大将军刘璩使于契丹。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0045",
          "zh": "冬十二月，宣义军节度使贺瑰为北面行营招讨使。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0046",
          "zh": "己巳，如西都卜郊。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0047",
          "zh": "晋人取杨刘。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0048",
          "zh": "四年正月，不克郊，己卯，至自西都。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0049",
          "zh": "夏四月己酉，尚书吏部侍郎萧顷为中书侍郎、同中书门下平章事。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0050",
          "zh": "己巳，赵光逢罢。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0051",
          "zh": "冬十二月庚子朔，贺瑰杀其将谢彦章、孟审澄、侯温裕。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0052",
          "zh": "癸亥，瑰及晋人战于胡柳，败绩。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0053",
          "zh": "是岁，泰宁军节度使张守进叛附于晋，亳州团练使刘寻阝为兖州安抚制置使以讨之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0054",
          "zh": "五年春正月，晋军于德胜。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0055",
          "zh": "秋八月乙未朔，开封尹王瓒为北面行营招讨使。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0056",
          "zh": "冬十月，刘寻阝克兖州，张守进伏诛。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0057",
          "zh": "十二月，晋人取濮阳。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0058",
          "zh": "天平军节度使霍彦威为北面行营招讨使。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0059",
          "zh": "六年夏四月己亥，降死罪以下囚。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0060",
          "zh": "乙巳，尚书左丞李琪为中书侍郎、同中书门下平章事。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0061",
          "zh": "河中节度使朱友谦袭同州，杀其节度使程全晖，叛附于晋，泰宁军节度使刘寻阝讨之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0062",
          "zh": "秋七月，陈州妖贼母乙自称天子。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0063",
          "zh": "九月庚寅，供奉官郎公远为契丹欢好使。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0064",
          "zh": "冬十月，母乙伏诛。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0065",
          "zh": "龙德元年春，赵将张文礼杀其君镕来乞师，不许。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0066",
          "zh": "三月丁亥朔，禁私度僧尼。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0067",
          "zh": "陈州刺史惠王友能反。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0068",
          "zh": "夏五月丙戌朔，德音改元，降流罪已下囚。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0069",
          "zh": "秋，赦友能，降封房陵侯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0070",
          "zh": "天平军节度使戴思远为北面行营招讨使。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0071",
          "zh": "冬十月，思远及晋人战于戚城，败绩。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0072",
          "zh": "二年春正月，思远袭魏州，取成安。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0073",
          "zh": "秋八月，滑州兵马留后段凝攻卫州，执其刺史李存儒。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0074",
          "zh": "戴思远克淇门、共城、新乡。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0075",
          "zh": "三年春三月，潞州李继韬叛于晋，来附。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0076",
          "zh": "夏闰四月，唐人取郓州。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0077",
          "zh": "五月庚申，宣义军节度使王彦章为北面行营招讨使，取德胜南城。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0078",
          "zh": "秋八月，段凝为北面行营招讨使。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0079",
          "zh": "先锋将康延孝叛降于唐。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0080",
          "zh": "冬十月甲戌，宣义军节度使王彦章及唐人战于中都，败绩，死之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0081",
          "zh": "唐人取曹州。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0082",
          "zh": "盗窃传国宝奔于唐。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0083",
          "zh": "戊寅，皇帝崩。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0084",
          "zh": "梁亡。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}